---
import HomeLayout from '../layouts/HomeLayout.astro';
---

<HomeLayout
  title="Arief Daffa - Web Developer"
  description="Arief Daffa is a web developer building polished, performant interfaces for products, portfolios, and digital tools."
  pathname="/"
>
<main id="top" class="site-shell">
  <section class="section hero">
    <div class="container hero-showcase">
      <div
        class="hero-panel"
        aria-label="Arief Daffa portfolio introduction"
      >
        <img
          class="hero-bg"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df0852?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=2400&amp;q=85"
          alt="Laptop workspace with code editor"
        />

        <div class="hero-center">
          <p>
            Every web interface I build begins with structure, evolves
            through design, and ships as a fast, focused experience.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero-title">Arief Daffa</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="social-grid" aria-label="Social profiles">
        <a
          class="social-card"
          href="https://github.com/AriefDaffa"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="social-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M12 .5A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 8.36 22.9c.58.1.79-.25.79-.56v-2.02c-3.22.7-3.9-1.38-3.9-1.38-.53-1.34-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.06-.72.08-.7.08-.7 1.17.08 1.79 1.2 1.79 1.2 1.04 1.78 2.73 1.27 3.4.97.1-.75.4-1.27.74-1.56-2.57-.29-5.27-1.28-5.27-5.72 0-1.27.45-2.3 1.2-3.11-.12-.3-.52-1.48.12-3.08 0 0 .98-.31 3.2 1.19a11.1 11.1 0 0 1 5.82 0c2.22-1.5 3.2-1.19 3.2-1.19.64 1.6.24 2.78.12 3.08.75.82 1.2 1.85 1.2 3.11 0 4.45-2.71 5.43-5.3 5.72.42.36.8 1.08.8 2.18v3.23c0 .31.2.67.8.56A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 12 .5Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="sr-only">GitHub</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="social-card"
          href="https://instagram.com/ariefdaffa"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="social-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M7.8 2h8.4A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 22 7.8v8.4a5.8 5.8 0 0 1-5.8 5.8H7.8A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 2 16.2V7.8A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 7.8 2Zm0 2A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 4 7.8v8.4A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 7.8 20h8.4a3.8 3.8 0 0 0 3.8-3.8V7.8A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 16.2 4H7.8Zm8.85 2.05a1.3 1.3 0 1 1 0 2.6 1.3 1.3 0 0 1 0-2.6ZM12 7.2a4.8 4.8 0 1 1 0 9.6 4.8 4.8 0 0 1 0-9.6Zm0 2a2.8 2.8 0 1 0 0 5.6 2.8 2.8 0 0 0 0-5.6Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="social-card"
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arief-daffa"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="social-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M4.98 3.5a2.5 2.5 0 1 1 0 5.001 2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5ZM3 9.75h4v11.5H3V9.75Zm6.25 0h3.84v1.57h.06c.53-1 1.84-2.06 3.78-2.06 4.04 0 4.79 2.66 4.79 6.12v5.87h-4v-5.2c0-1.24-.02-2.83-1.73-2.83-1.73 0-1.99 1.35-1.99 2.74v5.29h-4V9.75Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="social-card"
          href="https://dribbble.com/ariefdaffa"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="social-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 0 20 10 10 0 0 0 0-20Zm6.64 4.9a8.02 8.02 0 0 1 1.72 4.84 17.2 17.2 0 0 0-5.47-.26 29.1 29.1 0 0 0-.74-1.58 14.2 14.2 0 0 0 4.49-3Zm-6.64-3a8 8 0 0 1 5.23 1.94 12.4 12.4 0 0 1-3.93 2.58 35.6 35.6 0 0 0-2.75-4.36c.47-.1.96-.16 1.45-.16Zm-3.54.93a29.5 29.5 0 0 1 2.82 4.32 30.7 30.7 0 0 1-7.07.93 8.03 8.03 0 0 1 4.25-5.25ZM3.9 12v-.1a32.7 32.7 0 0 0 8.21-1.12c.22.43.42.87.61 1.31l-.31.1a12.75 12.75 0 0 0-6.18 4.66A7.96 7.96 0 0 1 3.9 12Zm8.1 8.1a7.95 7.95 0 0 1-4.37-1.3 10.9 10.9 0 0 1 5.76-4.78l.1-.03a33.2 33.2 0 0 1 1.48 5.63A7.92 7.92 0 0 1 12 20.1Zm4.78-1.55a35.2 35.2 0 0 0-1.36-5.03 14.8 14.8 0 0 1 4.76.33 8.03 8.03 0 0 1-3.4 4.7Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="sr-only">Dribbble</span>
        </a>
        <a class="social-card" href="mailto:hello@ariefdaffa.dev">
          <span class="social-icon" aria-hidden="true">@</span>
          <span class="sr-only">Email</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section dark-band">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="manifesto js-manifesto">
        Interfaces should feel deliberate, load quickly, guide attention,
        and make the product easier to trust. I build the visual layer and
        the engineering layer as one system.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section skill-showcase" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="skills-layout">
        <div class="skills-intro">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Skills</p>
          <h2>Tools I use to ship carefully.</h2>
          <p>
            A practical stack for building responsive product surfaces,
            maintainable components, and web apps that stay fast under real
            usage.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-rows">
          <article class="skill-row">
            <h3>Frontend engineering</h3>
            <div>
              <p>
                Component architecture, interaction details, accessibility,
                and performance-sensitive front ends.
              </p>
              <div class="skill-list">
                <span>React</span>
                <span>Next.js</span>
                <span>Astro</span>
                <span>TypeScript</span>
                <span>JavaScript</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="skill-row">
            <h3>Interface styling</h3>
            <div>
              <p>
                Detailed layouts, reusable design tokens, and expressive
                motion without sacrificing clarity.
              </p>
              <div class="skill-list">
                <span>TailwindCSS</span>
                <span>CSS</span>
                <span>GSAP</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="skill-row">
            <h3>Backend basics</h3>
            <div>
              <p>
                Enough server-side experience to collaborate cleanly across
                product boundaries.
              </p>
              <div class="skill-list">
                <span>Laravel</span>
                <span>Node.js</span>
                <span>Elysia.js</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="skill-row">
            <h3>Product workflow</h3>
            <div>
              <p>
                Git workflows, API integration, testing habits, and turning
                design references into working UI.
              </p>
              <div class="skill-list">
                <span>Git</span>
                <span>REST APIs</span>
                <span>Testing</span>
                <span>Web Vitals</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section timeline-section" id="timeline">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="timeline-head">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">History</p>
        <h2>Experiences</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline" aria-label="Career timeline">
        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-content left">
            <h3>Frontend Developer</h3>
            <p>
              CODE.ID, Jakarta. Contract role building production web
              interfaces in a hybrid setup.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-date">
            <span class="timeline-pill">12 - 25</span>
            <span class="timeline-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">
            <span class="timeline-pill">08 - 23</span>
            <span class="timeline-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content right">
            <h3>Frontend Web Developer</h3>
            <p>
              PT FAN Integrasi Teknologi. Built React features, refactored
              production code, and improved app stability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-content left">
            <h3>Software Engineer Intern</h3>
            <p>
              Tokopedia Web Platform. Worked on search components,
              debugging, tests, and performance improvement.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-date">
            <span class="timeline-pill">05 - 22</span>
            <span class="timeline-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">
            <span class="timeline-pill">01 - 22</span>
            <span class="timeline-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content right">
            <h3>Lead Frontend Developer</h3>
            <p>
              KawanBantu. Led frontend workflow, introduced tooling, and
              maintained a user-facing application.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-content left">
            <h3>Frontend Department</h3>
            <p>
              BCC Faculty of Computer Science, Brawijaya University. Grew
              through community engineering practice.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-date">
            <span class="timeline-pill">03 - 21</span>
            <span class="timeline-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section portfolio-section" id="work">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="portfolio-head">
        <div>
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Portfolio</p>
          <h2>My projects.</h2>
        </div>
        <a
          class="portfolio-button"
          href="/projects/"
        >
          See all
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-grid" aria-label="Featured portfolio projects">
        <a
          class="portfolio-card small js-scale-fade"
          href="/projects/byakuya/"
          aria-label="Open Byakuya project detail"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/project/byakuya.png"
            alt="Byakuya messaging app project preview"
          />
          <div class="portfolio-copy">
            <h3>Byakuya</h3>
            <p>Next.js, TypeScript, Elysia.js</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="portfolio-card small js-scale-fade"
          href="/projects/naya-living/"
          aria-label="Open Naya Living project detail"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/project/naya-living.png"
            alt="Naya Living design studio project preview"
          />
          <div class="portfolio-copy">
            <h3>Naya Living</h3>
            <p>Laravel, Alpine.js, TailwindCSS</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="portfolio-card feature js-scale-fade"
          href="/projects/btn-properti/"
          aria-label="Open BTN Properti project detail"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/project/btn-properti.png"
            alt="BTN Properti web portal project preview"
          />
          <div class="portfolio-copy">
            <h3>BTN Properti</h3>
            <p>2024 · Next.js property search portal</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="portfolio-card wide js-scale-fade"
          href="/projects/hoshi/"
          aria-label="Open Hoshi project detail"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/project/hoshi.png"
            alt="Hoshi anime streaming platform project preview"
          />
          <div class="portfolio-copy">
            <h3>Hoshi</h3>
            <p>React, TypeScript, shadcn/ui</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="portfolio-card small js-scale-fade"
          href="/projects/isf/"
          aria-label="Open IISF Website project detail"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/project/isf.png"
            alt="Indonesia Sustainability Forum website project preview"
          />
          <div class="portfolio-copy">
            <h3>IISF Website</h3>
            <p>Laravel, TailwindCSS</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="portfolio-card small js-scale-fade"
          href="/projects/lagalio/"
          aria-label="Open Lagalio project detail"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/project/lagalio.webp"
            alt="Lagalio Spotify playlist project preview"
          />
          <div class="portfolio-copy">
            <h3>Lagalio</h3>
            <p>React, TypeScript, Spotify API</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span>Astro</span>
      <span>React</span>
      <span>TypeScript</span>
      <span>Tailwind</span>
      <span>GSAP</span>
      <span>Accessibility</span>
      <span>Performance</span>
      <span>Design Systems</span>
      <span>Astro</span>
      <span>React</span>
      <span>TypeScript</span>
      <span>Tailwind</span>
      <span>GSAP</span>
      <span>Accessibility</span>
      <span>Performance</span>
      <span>Design Systems</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section blog-section" id="blog">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="portfolio-head">
        <div>
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Blog</p>
          <h2>Latest writing.</h2>
        </div>
        <a
          class="portfolio-button"
          href="/blog/"
        >
          See all
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="blog-grid" aria-label="Latest blog posts">
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span>August 7, 2024</span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Is it the end of the world?</h3>
            <p>
              Throughout history, humanity has been fascinated and terrified by
              the idea of the world's end.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="blog-card-footer"
            href="/blog/end-of-world/"
          >
            Read article <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span>July 10, 2024</span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Bocchi the Rock! – Anime Review</h3>
            <p>
              A delightful anime series about Hitori Gotou, a painfully shy
              high school girl who dreams of becoming a rock star.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="blog-card-footer"
            href="/blog/bocchi-the-rock-review/"
          >
            Read article <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span>July 6, 2024</span>
            <span>2 min read</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>How to Save Money: Practical Tips for a Better Financial Future</h3>
            <p>
              Simple strategies and mindful habits to start saving effectively
              and build a stronger financial future.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="blog-card-footer"
            href="/blog/saving-money/"
          >
            Read article <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section footer-section" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="footer-wordmark" aria-hidden="true">Arief Daffa</div>

        <div class="footer-grid">
          <div class="footer-contact">
            <div class="footer-socials" aria-label="Social links">
              <a
                href="https://instagram.com/ariefdaffa"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                aria-label="Instagram"
              >
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    d="M7.8 2h8.4A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 22 7.8v8.4a5.8 5.8 0 0 1-5.8 5.8H7.8A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 2 16.2V7.8A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 7.8 2Zm0 2A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 4 7.8v8.4A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 7.8 20h8.4a3.8 3.8 0 0 0 3.8-3.8V7.8A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 16.2 4H7.8Zm8.85 2.05a1.3 1.3 0 1 1 0 2.6 1.3 1.3 0 0 1 0-2.6ZM12 7.2a4.8 4.8 0 1 1 0 9.6 4.8 4.8 0 0 1 0-9.6Zm0 2a2.8 2.8 0 1 0 0 5.6 2.8 2.8 0 0 0 0-5.6Z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/AriefDaffa"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                aria-label="GitHub"
              >
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    d="M12 .5A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 8.36 22.9c.58.1.79-.25.79-.56v-2.02c-3.22.7-3.9-1.38-3.9-1.38-.53-1.34-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.06-.72.08-.7.08-.7 1.17.08 1.79 1.2 1.79 1.2 1.04 1.78 2.73 1.27 3.4.97.1-.75.4-1.27.74-1.56-2.57-.29-5.27-1.28-5.27-5.72 0-1.27.45-2.3 1.2-3.11-.12-.3-.52-1.48.12-3.08 0 0 .98-.31 3.2 1.19a11.1 11.1 0 0 1 5.82 0c2.22-1.5 3.2-1.19 3.2-1.19.64 1.6.24 2.78.12 3.08.75.82 1.2 1.85 1.2 3.11 0 4.45-2.71 5.43-5.3 5.72.42.36.8 1.08.8 2.18v3.23c0 .31.2.67.8.56A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 12 .5Z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arief-daffa"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                aria-label="LinkedIn"
              >
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    d="M4.98 3.5a2.5 2.5 0 1 1 0 5.001 2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5ZM3 9.75h4v11.5H3V9.75Zm6.25 0h3.84v1.57h.06c.53-1 1.84-2.06 3.78-2.06 4.04 0 4.79 2.66 4.79 6.12v5.87h-4v-5.2c0-1.24-.02-2.83-1.73-2.83-1.73 0-1.99 1.35-1.99 2.74v5.29h-4V9.75Z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            <p>Bekasi, Jawa Barat<br />Indonesia</p>
            <a href="mailto:hello@ariefdaffa.dev">hello@ariefdaffa.dev</a>
          </div>

          <div class="footer-column">
            <h3>Menu</h3>
            <a href="#top">About</a>
            <a href="/projects/">Projects</a>
            <a href="#services">Services</a>
            <a href="#timeline">Experience</a>
          </div>

          <div class="footer-column">
            <h3>Work</h3>
            <a href="/projects/">Portfolio</a>
            <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
            <a href="#services">Skills</a>
          </div>

          <div class="footer-column">
            <h3>Contact</h3>
            <a href="mailto:hello@ariefdaffa.dev">Email</a>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/AriefDaffa"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              >GitHub</a>
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arief-daffa"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              >LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="#contact">Start a project</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-rule">
          <a class="footer-cta" href="mailto:hello@ariefdaffa.dev"
            >Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
          <p class="footer-note">
            From product interfaces to personal websites. I build front-end
            systems that feel sharp, readable, and reliable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

</HomeLayout>
